title: Pending deployment created at <%= new Date().toISOString() %>
labels:
  - deployment
body: |
  The following changes have been detected from [<%= GITHUB_WORKFLOW %>](https://github.com/<%= GITHUB_REPOSITORY%>/actions/runs/<%= GITHUB_RUN_ID %>) in the infrastructure.

  <% changedStacks.map(stack => { %>
  <%= stack.plan.summary %><%= changedStacks.length > 1 ? ' for `' + stack.name + '`':'' %>
  ```<% stack.plan.changes.map(change => { %>
  <%= change %>
  <% }).join('\n') %>
  ```
  <% }).join('\n') %>

  Please review the changes and proceed with the deployment by adding `approved-deployment` label to the issue.

  - SHA: <%=GITHUB_SHA%>
  - Detected At: <%=new Date().toISOString()%>
  - From Workflow Run: [<%= GITHUB_WORKFLOW %>](https://github.com/<%= GITHUB_REPOSITORY%>/actions/runs/<%= GITHUB_RUN_ID %>)
